# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> (grubbing process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> "A mechanical vegetation removal process in which vegetation is uprooted by severing subsoil roots and prying or pulling the plant from the ground, using hand tools such as a spade, mattock, or root wrench."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4817-0423>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> "root wrench removal"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> "spading removal"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> "uprooting"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> "grubbing process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broadMatch> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> <https://w3id.org/elmo/cas/2.3>)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://w3id.org/elmo/property/hasCASCode> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> "2.3")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620022> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620021>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> (cut and cover removal process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> "A mechanical vegetation removal process during which plants at ground level are cut and residual stumps are covered with a sun-blocking material (e.g. silage tarp)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4817-0423>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> "solarization"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620023> "cut and cover removal process"@en)
