# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> (mowing process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> "A mechanical vegetation removal process in which a human uses a mower to cut vegetation to a defined height above ground level. The cut material may be left in place or collected and removed. Mowing is commonly used to manage grassland, meadow, and road verge vegetation."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> "Added following Delphi survey recommendations."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> "2026-03-18T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasBroadSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> "cutting removal process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> "mowing process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broadMatch> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> <https://w3id.org/elmo/cas/2.3>)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://w3id.org/elmo/property/hasCASCode> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621036> "2.3")
